  "description": [
    "6 Urge Thomas group be dumped CRC opens drive for petitions The antidemocratic role of the House UnAmerican Com mittee was laid bare this week by the Civil Rights Congress The CRC is collecting a half million signatures on petitions asking that a resolution by Rep Adolph Sabath D 111 which if passed by the House of Represen tatives would end the committees own unAmerican activities The antilakjgr Jewbaiting Ne grohating actions of the House unAmerican Committee were ex posed by the CRC in a pamphlet issued in connection with its call for a national conference on civil rights to be held here Nov 2123 THE pamphlet Americas Thought Police documents the Stars to report on red smear Several screen writers and actors involved in the recent Hollywood investigation by the House unAmerican Activi ties Committee will give Chi cagoans a firsthand account of their role in the Washington hearings the Illinois Chapter of the Civil Rights Congress announced today As participants in a public meeting to be sponsored by the Civil Rights Congress at Or chestra Hall on November 21 the Hollywood figures will join with Robert Morss Lovett for mer University of Chicago fac ulty member Dr Harry"
